<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
{% include 'head.twig' %}
<body>
    <div id="container">
        {% include 'header.twig' %}
        <p>
            Welcome to this <a href="https://remotestorage.io/">remoteStorage</a> server!
        </p>

        <p class="info">
            Connect to this service using the remoteStorage applet using <strong><em>user</em>@{{ host|e }}</strong>.
        </p>

        <p class="warning">
            <strong>NOTE</strong>: you need to have an account on this server to be able to use it! You can always <a href="https://github.com/fkooman/php-remote-storage/">run your own</a>!
        </p>

        <p>
            Use an application that supports <a href="https://remotestorage.io/">remoteStorage</a> 
            and connect with this service. Some applications you could use:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="https://sharesome.5apps.com/">Sharesome</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://webmarks.5apps.com/">Webmarks</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://remotestorage-browser.5apps.com/">remoteStorage Browser</a></li>   
            <li><a href="https://unterwaditzer.net/taskrs/">Taskrs</a></li>
        </ul>

        <p>
            <a href="https://wiki.remotestorage.io/Apps">Here</a> is a another 
            list of applications supporting 
            <a href="https://remotestorage.io/">remoteStorage</a>!
        </p>

    </div> <!-- /container -->
</body>
</html>
